formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.	The aforementioned information is certified on the basis of duly signed unaudited books of accounts of the firm as on 31-03-2020 and further information from provisional unaudited books of account upto 30-06-2020 and other information and explanation which to the best of my knowledge and belief were necessary for the purpose of issuing this certificate.
2.	Actual cost of construction incurred as per books of accounts included therein cost incurred in the nature of ?on- Site expenditure in the nature of development of project? and ?Payment of Taxes ?.
3.	The Firm had not maintained separate RERA Account. Further, regarding booking receipts received and withdrawals from current account as mentioned above, I have considered net deposits in bank account, of customer booking receipts and withdrawals out of the said bank account for the period 16/12/2019 to 30-06-2020.Receipts of Service tax and GST from customers is not included in above figures.
Withdrawals from bank accounts as seen in bank statement includes withdrawals out of-  
?	Capital of partners deposited in the said bank account and
?	Withdrawals out of deposits of customer booking advance.
?	Withdrawals out of loan disbursements made by the bank.
Thus, absolute maping of receipts from customers with withdrawals out of bank account is not possible.
4.	I am unable to certify the detail of Mobile No and PAN of the customer, since the necessary evidence is not in the possession of the firm. 
5.	The firm is not in possession of agreement to sale details and in absence of information, I have mentioned the date of sale deed executed instead of date of agreement to sale. Further, I am unable to certify as to whether the firm had entered registered Agreement for Sale with buyers on receipt of consideration in excess of 10% of the apartment value after enactment of Act. 
6.	In respect of the below mentioned flats, the firm had not entered into registered Agreement for Sale with buyers on receipt of consideration in excess of 10% of the apartment value after enactment of Act. Therefore, the date of agreement of sale is kept blank in the form-3(Annexure).
Flat no ? A-1,A-5,B-11,B-41,A-46,B-53,D-110,A-130,A-132,A-150,C-162 and A-177.
Further, I am assigned the certificate issue assignment for the first time for period under consideration. Relevant reliance is placed on the work of the previous professional for the continuity of the balances. It was found the the Opening balance of the Bank account showed some variance and the same has been added to deposits for the period after obtaining necessary explanations from the promoters.
There is a variance in the amount received from booked inventory as per books of accounts and as per RERA Sheet due to excess amount received on account of stamp duty charges and GST Collections.
